    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car at a reasonable price. The exterior shows its history with several noticeable scratches along the side panels and a few small dings on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear from regular use over the years. Mechanically, it starts reliably and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance for the suspension and brakes to keep it in top shape. It\u2019s an honest car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and preserved to exacting standards, every detail reflects a commitment to automotive excellence. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, original interior, this motorcar offers an unparalleled experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to witness the uncompromising quality and mechanical integrity of this exceptional acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this car. It is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this beauty since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every service was done right on schedule. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm sad to see it go, but I'd love for it to find a great new home where it'll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This example is mechanically flawless, boasting a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement. The chassis is structurally pristine with a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring the 3.2L inline-six\u2019s 333hp is delivered reliably through the Getrag 6-speed manual and M-Variable differential lock. Finished in original paint with zero track time, the suspension kinematics remain tight and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is razor-sharp. A truly turnkey masterpiece for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Interior flawless. Full service history included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2021 Porsche 718 Cayman is the definition of a 'collector grade' vehicle. Finished in a stunning Deep Sea Blue, the paint remains in showroom condition with a full front-end paint protection film and ceramic coating applied since day one\u2014absolutely zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains that new-car scent; the Black leather sport seats show no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by premium weather mats since purchase. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain, let alone snow. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at an authorized dealership, with all receipts and a clean, single-owner history provided. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the moment it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an exceptional vehicle maintained to the most exacting standards. This example remains in pristine, showroom condition, representing a level of preservation rarely encountered on the secondary market. From its flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior surfaces, every detail reflects meticulous ownership and uncompromising care. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning driver who demands mechanical and aesthetic excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It's in such incredible shape that you'd honestly think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I've meticulously cared for every inch of it, and it really shows\u2014it looks and drives like a total dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Come say hi and take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level FD3S RX-7, showcasing the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. This example retains its numbers-matching 13B-REW power unit, featuring the complex sequential twin-turbocharger system with seamless transition and robust boost pressure throughout the rev range. The chassis remains structurally flawless, benefiting from a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension setup and a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures surgical turn-in and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system overhaul and a comprehensive vacuum line refresh to ensure the integrity of the sequential solenoid system. The five-speed manual gearbox offers short, mechanical throws with crisp engagement, paired with a communicative clutch. This is a rare, unmolested specimen with factory-original paint and a cockpit free of typical plastics degradation, representing a turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
